sourceMeaningMnemonic: Let the <radical>sun</radical> shine into your <radical>ear</radical> while sitting on a <radical>stool</radical> and make sure <kanji>most</kanji> of it gets in your head. You want to fill your brain with the most sun anyone ever has.
meaningInfo: Most of the sun is getting into your ear, but not all of it. Darn, maybe you should try angling yourself a different way.
readingMnemonic: <kanji>Most</kanji> of this is for your <reading>cy</reading>borg (<ja>さい</ja>). You're testing out a new way to power it, but if you can't get most of the sun into your ear, it won't be enough to power most of the cyborg's robo-parts.
readingInfo: Install the part into your cyborg. As long as most of the sun gets into its human ear, most of its cyborg bits will have power.
